-- TAKE A LOOK-G20 finance ministers and central bankers meet in Australia
-- 
-- Sat Sep 20, 2014 08:47PM EDT
-- None



Sept 21 (Reuters) - Financial leaders of the Group of 20 top economies remain committed to chasing higher global growth, but were divided on how to achieve it as Germany pushed back at calls from the United States and others for more immediate stimulus.

